# Evidence records are committed byte-for-byte as run: their SHA-256 values
# are recorded in manifest.toml and inside transcript.txt, so line-ending
# normalization (the repository-wide `* text=auto` with core.autocrlf) would
# silently rewrite the hashed bytes on commit or checkout and break the
# recorded chain. transcript/report are CRLF as captured on the maintainer
# machine; the OEM and GMAT script are LF as the driver writes them.
transcript.txt -text
gmat_import_report.txt -text
twobody_leo.oem -text
twobody_leo_oem_import.script -text
